1022
01:01:01,989 --> 01:01:03,429
I promise.

1023
01:01:04,069 --> 01:01:06,709
You can talk to me
whenever you want, all right?

1024
01:01:07,749 --> 01:01:10,869
You remember when we talked
about little baby Jesus?

1025
01:01:11,829 --> 01:01:12,949
Remember that?

1026
01:01:13,189 --> 01:01:17,028
Well, I will be up there with Him.
And I will be watching you.

1027
01:01:20,229 --> 01:01:21,949
And I'll wait for you.

1028
01:01:23,669 --> 01:01:27,349
And if you want to talk to me anytime,
I will be there...

1029
01:01:27,588 --> 01:01:28,948
