1030
01:01:38,389 --> 01:01:41,148
I'll miss you so bad, honey.

1031
01:01:43,628 --> 01:01:45,789
I wrote you a letter.

1032
01:01:49,388 --> 01:01:51,069
And your mama will have it...

1033
01:01:51,308 --> 01:01:54,229
