- Who's that?
- Prisoners.

1054
01:03:38,947 --> 01:03:40,227
That's what they do.

1055
01:03:40,948 --> 01:03:43,428
Every word they say is a lie.

1056
01:03:44,067 --> 01:03:45,788
Well, everyone lies, pal.

1057
01:03:46,148 --> 01:03:48,188
I'm just here to write it down.

1058
01:03:50,227 --> 01:03:52,427
You've got 15 minutes, Mr. Everett...

1059
01:03:52,667 --> 01:03:54,627
...by order of Warden Plunkitt.
<i> Reporter arrives for an interview </i>

1060
01:03:55,908 --> 01:03:56,947
