1064
01:04:19,387 --> 01:04:20,467
So how's that girl?

1065
01:04:21,027 --> 01:04:22,827
The other, Michelle?

1066
01:04:23,267 --> 01:04:25,587
I heard she was in
some kind of accident?

1067
01:04:28,587 --> 01:04:30,547
Yeah, she was.

1068
01:04:31,867 --> 01:04:33,667
She was in a car wreck.

1069
01:04:33,947 --> 01:04:35,267
She didn't make it.

1070
01:04:36,627 --> 01:04:37,907
Oh, man.

