01:04:51,827 --> 01:04:54,467
...about how it feels to be in here.

1075
01:04:57,907 --> 01:04:59,987
Yeah, it's a human-interest piece.

1076
01:05:03,507 --> 01:05:04,986
I feel isolated.

1077
01:05:06,707 --> 01:05:07,827
I feel fear.

1078
01:05:09,067 --> 01:05:10,627
Fear of pain.

1079
01:05:12,307 --> 01:05:14,306
Fear of prison.

1080
01:05:15,507 --> 01:05:17,947
Fear of being separated
from my loved ones.

1081
01:05:19,906 --> 01:05:22,386
All those fears rolled up into one.

1082
01:05:24,466 --> 01:05:28,187
