1085
01:05:46,427 --> 01:05:49,226
...I believe in Jesus Christ,
our Lord and Savior.

1086
01:05:55,306 --> 01:05:58,387
I believe I'm going to a better place.

1087
01:06:00,547 --> 01:06:04,146
And there's a better place,
better justice there.

1088
01:06:05,546 --> 01:06:06,786
I came into my faith...

1089
