...late in life.

1090
01:06:10,226 --> 01:06:13,346
Did a lot of bad things
when I was younger. You know?

1091
01:06:14,706 --> 01:06:16,026
Anyway...

1092
01:06:17,546 --> 01:06:20,066
...I believe the crookeds will
be made straight.

1093
01:06:20,307 --> 01:06:23,386
That's what the Bible says.
I believe that.

1094
01:06:29,106 --> 01:06:31,026
So that's how I feel about it.

