01:06:34,386 --> 01:06:36,226
Is that all right, Mr. Everett?

1096
01:06:36,546 --> 01:06:37,826
You got nine more minutes.

1097
01:06:42,946 --> 01:06:45,226
I mean, is there any more
that you want?

1098
01:06:48,626 --> 01:06:50,786
Mr. Beechum, you don't know me.

1099
01:06:51,746 --> 01:06:54,066
I'm just a guy out there
with a screw loose.

1100
01:06:56,706 --> 01:06:59,586
Frankly, I don't give a rat's ass
about Jesus Christ...

1101
01:06:59,826 --> 01:07:02,826
...and I don't care about
justice in this world or the next.

1102
01:07:03,065 --> 01:07:05,786
I don't even care what's
right or wrong. Never have.

1103
01:07:06,625 --> 01:07:07,946
But you know what this is?

1104
01:07:10,065 --> 01:07:11,825
