1105
01:07:12,066 --> 01:07:14,746
No, it's no joke.
That's my nose.

1106
01:07:14,985 --> 01:07:18,506
To tell you the pitiful truth,
that's all I have in life.

1107
01:07:19,905 --> 01:07:21,786
When it tells me something stinks...

1108
01:07:22,026 --> 01:07:24,906
...I have faith in it,
like you have faith in Jesus.

1109
01:07:25,985 --> 01:07:30,026
