I know there's truth there somewhere.

1110
01:07:31,066 --> 01:07:32,586
But if it isn't working...

1111
01:07:33,186 --> 01:07:36,105
...you may as well drive me off
a cliff because I'm nothing.

1112
01:07:38,465 --> 01:07:39,306
Lately...

1113
01:07:39,866 --> 01:07:41,185
...I'm not 100% sure...

1114
01:07:41,425 --> 01:07:43,986
...my nose has been working that great.

1115
01:07:44,585 --> 01:07:46,265
So I've got to ask you...

1116
01:07:46,866 --> 01:07:48,666
...did you kill that woman or not?

1117
01:07:49,705 --> 01:07:50,625
