1120
01:08:04,745 --> 01:08:06,305
and you paid for it at the counter...

1121
01:08:06,585 --> 01:08:08,065
No, I never got it.

1122
01:08:08,705 --> 01:08:11,825
I told everybody this.
Why are you asking me this?

1123
01:08:13,425 --> 01:08:15,425
Tell it again. To me.

1124
01:08:20,545 --> 01:08:22,265
I went into the store...

1125
01:08:22,825 --> 01:08:25,105
...to buy a bottle of A-1 Sauce.

1126
01:08:25,825 --> 01:08:26,936
I didn't know where it was.

1127
01:08:26,937 --> 01:08:28,705
So I saw Amy standing
behind the counter.

1128
01:08:28,985 --> 01:08:29,852
- Hey, Amy.
- Hi Frank

1129
01:08:29,853 --> 01:08:31,345
Where you keep the steak sauce?

1130
01:08:31,625 --> 01:08:34,705
It's in the back. See where the
ketchup and relish is?

1131
01:08:35,665 --> 01:08:37,385
You know Frank I've been
meaning to talk to you.

1132
01:08:38,265 --> 01:08:39,745
I don't have it.

1133
01:08:40,025 --> 01:08:43,265
I mean I could give you 30 now,
but I don't have it all.

1134
01:08:44,065 --> 01:08:45,785
When can you give me the whole 96?

1135
01:08:47,265 --> 01:08:49,145
When I get paid, July 15th.

1136
01:08:49,465 --> 01:08:51,704
You're not gonna always
do me like this, are you?

1137
01:08:51,985 --> 01:08:56,545
No, I swear. It's just, the end of
school year. We have extra expenses.

1138
01:08:58,824 --> 01:09:00,305
All right, then.

1139
01:09:01,225 --> 01:09:02,145
July 15th?

1140
01:09:02,664 --> 01:09:03,985
July 15th.

1141
01:09:06,025 --> 01:09:07,265
Mind if I use the bathroom?

1142
01:09:07,625 --> 01:09:09,664
You know where it is, right?

1143
01:09:13,064 --> 01:09:15,185
So you weren't mad about the money?

1144
01:09:16,425 --> 01:09:19,065
I just wanted her to know I didn't
do business that way.

1145
01:09:19,345 --> 01:09:21,105
She was cool. I liked her.

1146
01:09:21,625 --> 01:09:23,025
- Were you carrying a gun?
- No

1147
01:09:25,984 --> 01:09:26,985
So then what?

1148
01:09:31,105 --> 01:09:33,985
I asked her, could I use her restroom.

1149
01:09:34,224 --> 01:09:37,825
I went in to use the restroom,
and the next thing I know...

1150
01:09:38,345 --> 01:09:39,824
...there was a gunshot.

1151
01:09:40,944 --> 01:09:41,945
That's all you got?

1152
01:09:42,225 --> 01:09:44,864
It's the Fourth of July
and we're not that busy.

1153
01:09:45,104 --> 01:09:46,664
- Give me the fucking chain!
- Not that!

1154
01:09:46,904 --> 01:09:48,544
Give me the fucking chain!

1155
01:10:02,664 --> 01:10:04,064
Oh, God. Amy!

1156
01:10:08,624 --> 01:10:09,784
Oh, Jesus!

1157
01:10:13,424 --> 01:10:14,464
Oh, God!

1158
01:10:16,944 --> 01:10:18,024
Sweet Jesus!

1159
01:10:21,104 --> 01:10:22,224
Can you breathe, Amy?

