hear the shots.

1178
01:11:43,113 --> 01:11:43,503
Mr Everett

1179
01:11:44,743 --> 01:11:46,383
I don't know. I don't know
anything that happened.

1180
01:11:46,623 --> 01:11:48,407
You don't know because
you don't know how long

1181
01:11:48,408 --> 01:11:50,304
you were on the floor
trying to save poor Amy's life.

1182
01:11:50,663 --> 01:11:53,783
