1186
01:12:00,623 --> 01:12:01,680
Alright that's it.

1187
01:12:01,681 --> 01:12:01,944
No

1188
01:12:02,863 --> 01:12:06,263
You believe us, don't you?
Do you believe us?

1189
01:12:06,983 --> 01:12:08,943
- Bonnie, don't.
