01:14:23,022 --> 01:14:24,742
What are you, a court
attorney or something?

1226
01:14:24,981 --> 01:14:25,941
Go ahead and hit a reporter.

1227
01:14:25,942 --> 01:14:27,382
See how long you keep
your god damn job.

1228
01:14:27,662 --> 01:14:30,142
- Why don't you get in the car?
