There's this boy sold
Warren a gun around that time.

1734
01:46:26,045 --> 01:46:27,444
This boy, he's in jail.

1735
01:46:27,724 --> 01:46:30,285
He might talk to them
if they give him time off.

1736
01:46:31,205 --> 01:46:34,085
Mrs. Russel, I could kiss you.

1737
01:46:34,844 --> 01:46:36,484
Release your hands.

1738
01:47:40,404 --> 01:47:42,044
Gun it, mister!

1739
01:47:42,324 --> 01:47:43,804
We go fast.

1740
