Pull over! Pull over
and stop the car!

1741
01:48:14,204 --> 01:48:15,844
Don't stop now!

1742
01:48:56,123 --> 01:48:58,003
Prepare yourself, all right?

1743
01:49:01,203 --> 01:49:03,243
I'm going to attempt this maneuver.

1744
01:49:19,923 --> 01:49:22,803
They really ought to do
something about that place.

1745
01:50:20,602 --> 01:50:22,762
Boy, something must be going on.

1746
01:50:23,123 --> 01:50:25,763
Maybe a fire, another accident
on the curve.

1747
01:50:49,882 --> 01:50:52,203
"To all whom it may concern,
be it known...

1748
