...whereas the Superior Court and
county of Alameda...

1749
01:50:55,442 --> 01:50:58,802
...ordered that Frank Louis Beechum
suffer the death penalty...

1750
01:50:59,082 --> 01:51:00,842
...within the walls of
San Quentin prison...

1751
01:51:01,122 --> 01:51:05,242
