01:53:03,001 --> 01:53:03,881
Go! Go!

1759
01:53:12,781 --> 01:53:16,891
Frank!

1760
01:53:19,399 --> 01:53:25,920
Frank!

1761
01:53:29,314 --> 01:53:31,314
Frank!

1762
01:54:02,400 --> 01:54:03,521
What's up? It's official,
it's for the kids.

1763
01:54:04,680 --> 01:54:06,161
I need some charity.

1764
01:54:07,681 --> 01:54:09,760
It's charity on toast, baby. Come on.

1765
01:54:10,040 --> 01:54:11,440
How you doing?

1766
01:54:13,841 --> 01:54:15,240
Thank you very much.

1767
01:54:15,920 --> 01:54:17,560
How you doing, sir?

1768
01:54:20,138 --> 01:54:21,990
Hey Ev! Kate like that dalmatian?

1769
01:54:22,280 --> 01:54:23,281
She loved it.

1770
01:54:23,720 --> 01:54:26,600
Even my ex managed to muster up
a little enthusiasm.

1771
01:54:27,121 --> 01:54:29,840
In fact I've got to get something
better for Christmas.

1772
01:54:30,080 --> 01:54:33,120
Sheepdog, collie,
we got Saint Bernards...

1773
01:54:33,400 --> 01:54:34,801
How about a hippopotamus?

1774
01:54:36,520 --> 01:54:40,200
Check it out! Local designer,
based on the one at the zoo.

1775
01:54:41,400 --> 01:54:43,960
Yeah, this is a beauty.

1776
01:54:44,920 --> 01:54:46,760
Think a homeless man can afford this?

1777
01:54:47,040 --> 01:54:48,760
You're not homeless.

1778
01:54:49,200 --> 01:54:51,600
Well, I'm wifeless and jobless...

1779
01:54:52,720 --> 01:54:54,440
...and I live in a hotel.

1780
01:54:56,000 --> 01:54:57,080
That's unless...

1781
01:54:57,480 --> 01:55:00,040
