these days.

1793
01:55:35,040 --> 01:55:37,400
Give me some charity, baby.
It's for the kids.

1794
01:55:38,799 --> 01:55:40,039
It's official!

1795
01:55:40,439 --> 01:55:43,680
I need some charity on toast!
Come over here, help me out.

1796
01:55:45,793 --> 01:55:46,760
Steve!

1797
01:55:49,079 --> 01:55:50,479
I know you got some charity.

1798
01:55:50,719 --> 01:55:52,440
You famous baby! Rich and famous.

1799
01:55:52,679 --> 01:55:56,280
I know you got charity on toast.
Give me some charity. Come on.

1800
01:55:56,560 --> 01:55:57,879
It's for the kids.

1801
01:55:58,119 --> 01:55:59,239
That's right, come on.

1802
01:55:59,519 --> 01:56:01,640
Give me 20, give me 100.
Come on, Steve.

1803
01:56:02,040 --> 01:56:04,479
Take it before my wife does,
and get out of here.

1804
01:56:04,759 --> 01:56:05,519
A 10?

1805
01:56:05,799 --> 01:56:08,158
Steve, you got more than that.
Come on, now. It's for the kids.

1806
01:56:08,159 --> 01:56:09,559
It's official.
Come on give some more

1807
